    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust patches, large dents, and peeling clear coat, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and a non-functional dashboard display. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention as it has a persistent engine knock and a transmission that slips during gear changes. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources into repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
      "price": 6500.0,
